      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sound BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine. This unit exhibits a linear power band and crisp actuation from the individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is robust, featuring a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-differential with no detectable lash. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and professional reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to mitigate floor fatigue. The suspension geometry is maintained via refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the chassis remains communicative during high-lateral-G cornering. While the exterior shows minor road-rash consistent with its mileage, the internals are optimized for performance longevity.",
